{"tid":394310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實民主牆曾幾何時係中共憲法規定既權利","createTime":"2017-09-09T21:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T16:15:40.000Z","uid":36901,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"851ebcf4e1331c445c8a0b5c485f206ee8e4c9cc","tid":394310,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T21:46:56.000Z","msg":"民主牆前身係乜就係大字報<br />\n1975-1982年的中共憲法<br />\n規定大字報係人民權利<br />\n1978年更出現西單民主牆運動<br />\n中共開始感到大字報危及政權<br />\n遂拉人封鋪<br />\n1982年更取消大字報憲法中法定權利<br />\n89學運期間民主牆再度活躍<br />\n成為批判中共既先鋒<br />\n不過89屠城後<br />\n一切又復歸平靜<br />\n反而民主牆係香港開花結果<br />\n每一次民主牆活躍<br />\n就必有政治運動跟隨<br />\n所以民主牆其實係中共眼中釘<br />\nnds學識用民主牆<br />\n對中共黎講都唔係乜好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5009050c2f9473c885762225080d1c789c7af1e3","tid":394310,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T21:50:17.000Z","msg":"西單民主牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://aiyuan.files.wordpress.com/2012/07/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faiyuan.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F07%2F2.jpg&h=dc87549d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76fca85637a4cbf8fd4e2af4b793a47d25da5e4b","tid":394310,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T21:54:54.000Z","msg":"1989既北大民主牆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2017/06/1989-%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%89%E9%96%80-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B-20170604064225_2c07_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2017%2F06%2F1989-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2596%2580-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B-20170604064225_2c07_small.jpg&h=a12e6960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1049fd8a72fd80802d75e7bbbda3bfe26534e9f8","tid":394310,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T01:27:13.000Z","msg":"俾支那知道支那人係民主牆貼嘢拉返上去打靶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加個「我是內地人，但支那獨立」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令啲支那人迅速消失"},{"pid":"0cd3cae31057cc01fa903dbc37f7c7d4bd1b1dee","tid":394310,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T01:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c967bd6eedea35941b88c3026355466a12fc29ff","tid":394310,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef49b2f2d44c34da8693677955853c51cbc361d","tid":394310,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"中國古代都有 叫華表"},{"pid":"fc84e88b46440444bf38a0855a0b162a4e8d2e6a","tid":394310,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國古代都有 叫華表</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb348591b4898216026ac4ed74cfb04edf95aa0","tid":394310,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Z1X7u65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ1X7u65.jpg&h=07b7bd76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a3f9e9d785c34ca1a764a511f587b8396c13cee","tid":394310,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:58:03.000Z","msg":"教d 陸生用民主牆<br />\n唔好理佢地貼咩，等佢地習慣抵抗暴政爭取自己權益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ea8c282cb4a173a7b7095feb679e042844023e","tid":394310,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><